videos.description: Fresno State's Marvelle Harris throws up a wild air ball, but Cezar Guerrero makes the heads-up play to get the rebound and get behind the 3-point line to hit the shot at the buzzer and send the Bulldogs to overtime at San Diego State.
videos.headline: Guerrero's crazy buzzer-beater sends Fresno State to OT
